WEBVTT

01:35:36.774 --> 01:35:39.233
You and your family walked free
from that boy's murder case

01:35:39.441 --> 01:35:40.441
by sheer luck!

01:35:40.899 --> 01:35:42.649
And then a bunch
of filthy news channels

01:35:42.691 --> 01:35:44.483
turned you into
some kind of hero.

01:35:45.149 --> 01:35:46.816
Don't let all that fame
go to your head.
